 Bride of Boogedy 
 Mr. Boogedy  is a 1986  made-for-television   family film , [1]  and failed  pilot [2]  directed by  Oz Scott  and written by Michael Janover, which originally aired as an episode of " The Disney Sunday Movie ." It tells the story of a gag gift salesman and his family 